data.name: Infinitrack Drag Shovel
data.desc: You can Tribute 1 EARTH Machine monster; Special Summon this card from your hand in Defense Position. You can banish 1 Machine monster from your GY; add 1 "Spin Turn" from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Infinitrack Drag Shovel" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
